@*
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      ملاحظات مهمة:
      • لا يوجد أي تعديل على الـ Backend.
      • تم الإبقاء على نفس بنية الـ Razor و asp-* helpers والـ CSS classes الأصلية.
      • التحسينات كلها على طبقة العرض (CSS + Vanilla JS باستخدام Native APIs فقط).
      • Navbar: الأقسام تظهر دائماً على الكمبيوتر، وعلى الموبايل عند الضغط على زر الشرائط.
      • Footer: محسّن بنفس لغة التصميم (زجاجي، تدرّجات، حركات لطيفة).
      • Skip-to-content + Back-to-top + Sticky scroll shadow.
      • الـ Script لا يحقن HTML ولا يستخدم eval → آمن من XSS.
      • يحترم prefers-reduced-motion للمستخدمين.
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*@
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Summer Courses Portal </title>

    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="~/favicon.svg" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" sizes="32x32" href="~/favicon.ico" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="~/apple-touch-icon.png" asp-append-version="true" />


    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ubuntu:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Oswald:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/enterprise.css" asp-append-version="true" />

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
         ENHANCED LAYOUT VISUAL LAYER (CSS)
    ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <style>
        /* ========== Skip link (accessibility) ========== */
        .lyt-skip{
            position: absolute; right: 12px; top: -60px;
            background: #072C2C; color: #fff; padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;
            z-index: 2000; transition: top .3s ease;
        }
        .lyt-skip:focus{ top: 12px; outline: 2px solid #FF5F03; outline-offset: 2px; }

        /* ========== NAVBAR — Glass + Underline + Mobile Drawer ========== */
        .navbar-enterprise{
            --nv-ease: cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1);
            --nv-bounce: cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
            --nv-primary: #072C2C;
            --nv-primary-2: #1e6b6b;
            --nv-accent: #FF5F03;
            --nv-glass-bg: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
            --nv-glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,.65);
            --nv-shadow: 0 10px 30px -16px rgba(7,44,44,.25);
            --nv-grad-primary: linear-gradient(135deg,#072C2C 0%,#1e6b6b 100%);
            --nv-grad-accent:  linear-gradient(135deg,#FF5F03 0%,#ffb060 100%);
            --nv-grad-mix:     linear-gradient(120deg,#072C2C,#1e6b6b 40%,#FF5F03);

            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1030;
            background: var(--nv-glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(150%);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(150%);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--nv-glass-border);
            box-shadow: var(--nv-shadow);
            transition: box-shadow .35s ease, background .35s ease;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise.nv-scrolled{
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 40px -18px rgba(7,44,44,.35);
        }
        .navbar-enterprise::after{
            content:""; position:absolute; left:0; right:0; bottom:-1px; height:2px;
            background: var(--nv-grad-mix); opacity:.55;
        }

        .navbar-enterprise .nav-container{
            display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
            gap: 14px; padding: 12px 22px;
            max-width: 1320px; margin:0 auto; position: relative;
        }

        /* Brand */
        .navbar-enterprise .navbar-brand-logo{
            display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;
            text-decoration:none; color: var(--nv-primary);
            transition: transform .35s var(--nv-ease);
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .navbar-brand-logo:hover{ transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .navbar-enterprise .brand-icon{
            width:46px; height:46px; border-radius:14px;
            display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
            color:#fff; font-size:1.15rem;
            background: var(--nv-grad-primary);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 22px -10px rgba(7,44,44,.55);
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform .5s var(--nv-bounce), box-shadow .35s ease;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .brand-icon::after{
            content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 30%, rgba(255,255,255,.45) 50%, transparent 70%);
            transform: translateX(-100%); transition: transform .8s ease;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .navbar-brand-logo:hover .brand-icon{
            transform: rotate(-8deg) scale(1.06);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 30px -10px rgba(7,44,44,.6);
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .navbar-brand-logo:hover .brand-icon::after{ transform: translateX(100%); }
        .navbar-enterprise .brand-text-main{
            font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height:1.1;
            background-image: var(--nv-grad-mix); background-size: 220% auto;
            -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; letter-spacing:.2px;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .brand-text-sub{
            font-size:.78rem; color:#475569; font-weight:600; margin-top:2px;
        }

        /* Mobile toggle */
        .navbar-enterprise .mobile-toggle{
            display: none;
            width:44px; height:44px; border-radius:12px;
            align-items:center; justify-content:center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(7,44,44,.15);
            background: #fff; color: var(--nv-primary);
            font-size: 1.05rem; cursor:pointer;
            transition: transform .3s var(--nv-ease), box-shadow .3s ease, background .3s ease, color .3s ease;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .mobile-toggle:hover{
            background: var(--nv-primary); color:#fff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 22px -10px rgba(7,44,44,.5);
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .mobile-toggle[aria-expanded="true"]{
            background: var(--nv-primary); color:#fff;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .mobile-toggle i{ transition: transform .35s var(--nv-ease); }
        .navbar-enterprise .mobile-toggle[aria-expanded="true"] i{ transform: rotate(90deg); }

        /* Desktop menu (always visible on desktop) */
        .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse{ display:flex; align-items:center; }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise{
            list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0;
            display:flex; align-items:center; gap: 6px;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-item{ position: relative; }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link{
            position: relative;
            display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
            padding: 10px 16px; font-weight: 700; font-size:.95rem;
            color: #1f2937; text-decoration:none; border-radius: 12px;
            transition: color .3s ease, background .3s ease, transform .3s var(--nv-ease);
            overflow: hidden; z-index: 1;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link .nav-icon{
            font-size:.95rem; color: var(--nv-primary-2);
            transition: transform .4s var(--nv-bounce), color .3s ease;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link::after{
            content:""; position:absolute; left:14px; right:14px; bottom:6px;
            height:2px; border-radius:2px;
            background: var(--nv-grad-accent);
            transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: right;
            transition: transform .45s var(--nv-ease);
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link::before{
            content:""; position:absolute; inset:0; border-radius:inherit;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(7,44,44,.06), rgba(255,95,3,.06));
            opacity:0; transition: opacity .35s ease; z-index:-1;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link:hover{ color: var(--nv-primary); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link:hover::after{ transform: scaleX(1); transform-origin: left; }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link:hover::before{ opacity:1; }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link:hover .nav-icon{
            transform: rotate(-8deg) scale(1.12); color: var(--nv-accent);
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link:focus-visible{
            outline: 2px solid var(--nv-accent); outline-offset: 3px;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link.active,
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link[aria-current="page"]{ color: var(--nv-primary); }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link.active::after,
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link[aria-current="page"]::after{
            transform: scaleX(1); transform-origin: left;
        }
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link.active::before,
        .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link[aria-current="page"]::before{ opacity:1; }

        /* Mobile drawer */
        @@media (max-width: 991.98px){
            .navbar-enterprise .mobile-toggle{ display:inline-flex; }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse{
                position: absolute; left: 14px; right: 14px; top: calc(100% + 10px);
                display: block;
                background: rgba(255,255,255,.96);
                backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(150%);
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(150%);
                border: 1px solid var(--nv-glass-border);
                border-radius: 18px;
                box-shadow: 0 24px 50px -18px rgba(7,44,44,.28);
                padding: 10px; overflow: hidden;
                max-height: 0; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-8px);
                transition: max-height .45s var(--nv-ease), opacity .35s ease, transform .35s ease, padding .3s ease;
                pointer-events: none;
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse.show,
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse.nv-open{
                max-height: 70vh; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); pointer-events: auto;
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse.collapsing{
                display:block; opacity:1; transform: translateY(0); pointer-events:auto;
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise{ flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; gap: 4px; }
            .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link{
                padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 12px;
                justify-content: flex-start; border: 1px solid transparent;
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link::after{
                left: 12px; right: auto; bottom: 50%;
                width: 3px; height: 0; border-radius: 3px;
                background: var(--nv-grad-accent);
                transform: none; transition: height .35s var(--nv-ease), top .35s ease, bottom .35s ease;
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link:hover::after,
            .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link.active::after,
            .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link[aria-current="page"]::after{
                height: 60%; bottom: 20%;
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .nav-enterprise-link:hover{
                border-color: rgba(7,44,44,.08); transform: translateX(-3px);
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse.show .nav-enterprise-item,
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse.nv-open .nav-enterprise-item{
                animation: nv-slideIn .45s var(--nv-ease) both;
            }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse .nav-enterprise-item:nth-child(1){ animation-delay:.05s; }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse .nav-enterprise-item:nth-child(2){ animation-delay:.12s; }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse .nav-enterprise-item:nth-child(3){ animation-delay:.19s; }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse .nav-enterprise-item:nth-child(4){ animation-delay:.26s; }
            .navbar-enterprise .navbar-collapse .nav-enterprise-item:nth-child(5){ animation-delay:.33s; }
        }

        @@keyframes nv-slideIn {
            from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(-8px); }
            to   { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* ========== FOOTER — Premium dark with aurora ========== */
        .footer-enterprise{
            --ft-primary: #072C2C;
            --ft-primary-2: #1e6b6b;
            --ft-accent: #FF5F03;
            --ft-grad-primary: linear-gradient(135deg,#072C2C 0%,#1e6b6b 100%);
            --ft-grad-accent:  linear-gradient(135deg,#FF5F03 0%,#ffb060 100%);
            --ft-grad-mix:     linear-gradient(120deg,#072C2C,#1e6b6b 40%,#FF5F03);
            --ft-ease: cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1);

            position: relative; overflow: hidden; isolation: isolate;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            background:
              radial-gradient(60% 60% at 80% 0%, rgba(255,95,3,.16), transparent 60%),
              radial-gradient(60% 60% at 10% 100%, rgba(30,107,107,.22), transparent 60%),
              linear-gradient(160deg, #051d1d 0%, #072C2C 60%, #0a3a3a 100%);
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
        .footer-enterprise::before{
            content:""; position:absolute; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:-1;
            background-image:
              linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
              linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 44px 44px;
            mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #000 30%, transparent 75%);
            -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #000 30%, transparent 75%);
        }
        /* Top wave */
        .footer-enterprise::after{
            content:""; position:absolute; left:0; right:0; top:-1px; height:60px;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 1440 60' preserveAspectRatio='none'><path fill='%23072C2C' d='M0,30 C240,60 480,0 720,30 C960,60 1200,0 1440,30 L1440,0 L0,0 Z'/></svg>") no-repeat top center / cover;
            transform: translateY(-100%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .footer-enterprise .footer-main{ padding: 60px 22px 28px; }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-container{ max-width: 1320px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-grid{
            display: grid; gap: 32px;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr));
        }

        .footer-enterprise .footer-col{
            opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: ft-fadeUp .8s var(--ft-ease) forwards;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-col:nth-child(1){ animation-delay: .05s; }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-col:nth-child(2){ animation-delay: .15s; }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-col:nth-child(3){ animation-delay: .25s; }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-col:nth-child(4){ animation-delay: .35s; }

        @@keyframes ft-fadeUp {
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .footer-enterprise .footer-col-title{
            font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff;
            margin: 0 0 18px; padding-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-col-title i{
            width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 10px;
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            background: var(--ft-grad-accent);
            color: #fff; font-size: .95rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -8px rgba(255,95,3,.55);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-col-title::after{
            content:""; position: absolute; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            width: 60px; height: 2px; border-radius: 2px;
            background: var(--ft-grad-accent);
            transition: width .5s var(--ft-ease);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-col:hover .footer-col-title::after{ width: 110px; }

        .footer-enterprise .footer-link{
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            color: #cbd5e1; text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: .92rem; font-weight: 600;
            transition: color .3s ease, background .3s ease, transform .3s var(--ft-ease), padding .3s ease;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-link i{
            font-size: .8rem; color: var(--ft-accent);
            transition: transform .35s var(--ft-ease);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-link:hover{
            color: #fff;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
            transform: translateX(-4px);
            padding-right: 14px;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-link:hover i{ transform: translateX(-3px) scale(1.1); }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-link:focus-visible{
            outline: 2px solid var(--ft-accent); outline-offset: 2px;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-text{
            color: #94a3b8; font-size: .88rem; line-height: 1.7;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        /* Social buttons */
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn{
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 14px; text-decoration: none;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
            color: #e2e8f0;
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform .35s var(--ft-ease), box-shadow .35s ease, background .35s ease, border-color .35s ease;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn::after{
            content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 30%, rgba(255,255,255,.18) 50%, transparent 70%);
            transform: translateX(-100%); transition: transform .8s ease; pointer-events:none;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn:hover{
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px -12px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn:hover::after{ transform: translateX(100%); }
        .footer-enterprise .social-icon{
            width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 12px;
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem; color: #fff;
            transition: transform .4s var(--ft-ease);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn:hover .social-icon{ transform: rotate(-8deg) scale(1.08); }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn.whatsapp .social-icon{
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25D366, #128C7E);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -8px rgba(37,211,102,.6);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn.facebook .social-icon{
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1877F2, #0a4fbb);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -8px rgba(24,119,242,.6);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn.whatsapp:hover{
            background: rgba(37,211,102,.10);
            border-color: rgba(37,211,102,.35);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-btn.facebook:hover{
            background: rgba(24,119,242,.10);
            border-color: rgba(24,119,242,.35);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-label-sub{
            font-size: .72rem; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 600;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .social-label-main{
            font-size: 1rem; color: #fff; font-weight: 800;
        }

        /* Developer badge */
        .footer-enterprise .dev-badge{
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
            padding: 14px;
            background:
              linear-gradient(rgba(7,44,44,.7), rgba(7,44,44,.7)) padding-box,
              var(--ft-grad-mix) border-box;
            border: 1.5px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: transform .4s var(--ft-ease), box-shadow .4s ease;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .dev-badge:hover{
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px -16px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
        }
        .footer-enterprise .dev-badge-icon{
            width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 14px;
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            background: var(--ft-grad-primary);
            color: #fff; font-size: 1.15rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -8px rgba(7,44,44,.7);
            transition: transform .5s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .dev-badge:hover .dev-badge-icon{ transform: rotate(-10deg) scale(1.08); }
        .footer-enterprise .dev-badge-text{
            font-size: .75rem; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        /* Divider + copyright */
        .footer-enterprise .footer-divider{
            border: 0; height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,.18), transparent);
            margin: 8px 22px 0;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-copyright{
            text-align: center;
            padding: 22px 22px 26px;
            color: #94a3b8; font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;
        }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-copyright i{ color: var(--ft-accent); }
        .footer-enterprise .footer-copyright span{
            color: #fff; font-weight: 800;
            background: var(--ft-grad-accent);
            -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        /* ========== Back to top button ========== */
        .lyt-totop{
            position: fixed; bottom: 22px; left: 22px; z-index: 1040;
            width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,#072C2C 0%,#1e6b6b 100%);
            color: #fff; border: none; cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 30px -10px rgba(7,44,44,.55);
            opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px) scale(.9);
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity .35s ease, transform .45s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1), box-shadow .35s ease;
        }
        .lyt-totop.is-visible{
            opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); pointer-events: auto;
        }
        .lyt-totop:hover{
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 40px -14px rgba(7,44,44,.7);
        }
        .lyt-totop:focus-visible{
            outline: 2px solid #FF5F03; outline-offset: 3px;
        }

        /* ========== Reduced motion ========== */
        @@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
            .navbar-enterprise *, .navbar-enterprise *::before, .navbar-enterprise *::after,
            .footer-enterprise *, .footer-enterprise *::before, .footer-enterprise *::after,
            .lyt-totop{
                animation: none !important;
                transition: none !important;
            }
            .footer-enterprise .footer-col{ opacity: 1; transform: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <a href="#main-content" class="lyt-skip">تخطّي إلى المحتوى الرئيسي</a>

    <nav class="navbar-enterprise" role="navigation" aria-label="القائمة الرئيسية">
        <div class="nav-container">

